resolver_getInfoByCode

ResultModel resolver_getInfoByCode(java.lang.String SID,
                                   java.lang.String RID)
Given the SID and RID of a code, resolve to get the result

参数：
SID - SID of the code, used to identify what standard the code belong to
RID - RID of the code, used to distinguish each code of the same standard, it's unique
返回：
the information related to the code, mostly URL or IP

返回：
the regular expression
